<li><a href="/scp-5059">SCP-5059</a> (&quot;Roll Out!&quot;)by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hammermaiden" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1552358); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1552358&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585502221" alt="HammerMaiden" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1552358)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hammermaiden" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1552358); return false;">HammerMaiden</a></span>!</li>
<li><a href="/a-song-that-is-unfortunately-about-toes">Single:untitled</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oboebandgeek99" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1782920); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1782920&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585502221" alt="Oboebandgeek99" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1782920)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/oboebandgeek99" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1782920); return false;">Oboebandgeek99</a></span> and <a href="/scp-5808">SCP-5808</a> (&quot;Immaculate Misconception&quot;) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585502221" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255688); return false;">DrAkimoto</a></span>, tied for third!!</li>
