														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4572423">
									

<p>The 2020&#160;144-Hour Jam Contest Two THEME GRAND PRIZE goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187885); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585588307" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4187885); return false;">Rounderhouse</a></span>, who submitted an entry for each theme and secured a total of 396 upvotes :</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-5983">SCP-5983</a> (&quot;Nuke York, Nuke York&quot;) (+140) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Theme 1</span></li>
<li><a href="/adoption-poster-pearl">Adoption Poster: Pearl!</a> (+117) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Theme 2</span></li>
<li><a href="/scp-5149">SCP-5149</a> (&quot;None of us are blind, Joe&quot;) (+139) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 3×2</span></li>
</ul>
<p>The 2020&#160;144-Hour Jam Contest Two FORMAT GRAND PRIZE goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585588307" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span>, who submitted an SCP, Tale, and GoI Format and secured a total of 175 upvotes :</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/cool-guys-dont-look-at-explosions">Cool Guys Don't Look At Explosions</a> (+82) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Theme 1</span></li>
<li><a href="/project-proposal-2018-145">Project Proposal 2018-145: &quot;a man's duty&quot;</a> (+52) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Theme 2</span></li>
<li><a href="/scp-5047">SCP-5047</a> (&quot;Apartment Hunting&quot;) (+41) <span style="font-size:smaller;">for Day 3×2</span></li>
</ul>
<p>Congratulations to the winners! Thank you to everyone who participated, and especial thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4037075); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4037075&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585588307" alt="Elogee FishTruck" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4037075)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4037075); return false;">Elogee FishTruck</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4463776); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4463776&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585588307" alt="N_Aepic_Fael" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4463776)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4463776); return false;">N_Aepic_Fael</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1585588307" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4916887); return false;">MalyceGraves</a></span> for collecting and tallying up the final scores!</p>

							</div>

								
